Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我和樱出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买完东西在常去的公园等你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12点见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 凛 我知道你们两个想单独享受休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么会出现我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是两个女生去购物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会逛很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是让我拿东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12点在公园哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点来早了 但没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就慢慢等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.84,0:01:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:01:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 只是有点头疼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会做饭来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我来店里打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也太不给面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去拜托那小子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎比较会做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心热血上头了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工具还挺全的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厨师突然来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家店的东西出名的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难找到人代替呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦 Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,11点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须回一趟集合地点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么熟人会出现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明只想和宗一郎大人品个茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉浑身不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caster 和场所无关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样两人在一起比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗一郎大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点单来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个热三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样继续拜托啦 Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方居然会有咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 已经中午了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是无处不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archer 你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你体谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎一言难尽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗一郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 推荐的蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先是酱汁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大蒜切末 加橄榄油翻炒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入西红柿罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打碎的法式清汤料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加盐 胡椒 砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溶入黄油完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洋葱切丁 香菇切薄片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡胸肉切丁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为鸡肉炒饭的料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用炒锅翻炒鸡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加洋葱 香菇 继续翻炒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入盐 粗胡椒 打碎的法式清汤料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻匀 炒去酸味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加白米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用切的手法拌匀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要烧焦 让酱汁渗入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后是蛋饼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炒锅加橄榄油 黄油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加盐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒入搅匀的蛋液
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边用筷子搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边摇锅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做成半熟状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半熟以后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推到炒锅的一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把蛋的封口处弄到上面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖在鸡肉炒饭上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,软软的蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口感精致细腻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有种温柔的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个居然是Archer做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然也会做饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个味道我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎没发觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从樱那里借来 稍微打扮了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在店里发现你的时候 感觉很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就进来看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樱说她就不用了 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在厨房里的样子很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说碰头的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙告诉了我原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约定也是我强加给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 在咖啡店帮忙感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么奇怪的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你还在在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saber刚才吃的 下次做给我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就一笔勾销
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论多少都做给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我在咖啡店吃了Archer做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 Saber 今晚再加两道菜
